                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strong, well-defined triceps are key to powerful arms and upper-body strength. The single-arm overhead tricep extension is a fantastic exercise for isolating and strengthening these muscles. </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">By focusing on one arm at a time, you ensure balanced muscle development and avoid imbalances. This guide will walk you through proper techniques, expert tips, and the ideal duration for the best results.</span></p>                    </div>
